{"word":"πῆχυς","slug":"πῆχυς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πῆχυς, εως, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>] <b>cubit,</b> a measure of length ranging from 45 to 52 centimeters or about 18 inches <b><a href='B:470 6:27'>Mt 6:27</a>; <a href='B:490 12:25'>Lk 12:25</a>; <a href='B:500 21:8'>J 21:8</a>; <a href='B:730 21:17'>Rv 21:17</a>.</b> Some take <b><a href='B:470 6:27'>Mt 6:27</a>; <a href='B:490 12:25'>Lk 12:25</a></b> in sense of addition to one’s lifespan. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πήρωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πιάζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}